&lt;p style="text-align: justify;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #808080; font-size: xx-small;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;* Saiba mais sobre IPv6, &lt;a href="http://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ipv6" target="_blank"&gt;aqui&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 21 Sep 2010 10:16:44 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/alog-migra-150-clientes-para-o-ipv6</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/furusho/blog/alog-migra-150-clientes-para-o-ipv6</guid></item></channel></rss>